I can check now; I’ll list the top-level folders inside Coin and report back.

## Next step
- I’m going to run a directory listing for Coin to show only its immediate subfolders.

<TASKS>
{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "type": "run_command",
      "cwd": ".",
      "command": "[ -d Coin ] && ls -1p Coin | grep '/$' | sed 's:/$::' || echo '__COIN_DIR_NOT_FOUND__'"
    }
  ]
}
